# Stray Go build outputs when `go build ./...` is run from repo root
# (Go names the binary after the last path segment — here `cmd` — which
# collides with apps/*/cmd dirs). Negation re-allows the cmd/ directory
# that now hosts top-level binaries (cmd/seed-definitions etc).
/cmd
